Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.82,0:00:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛逝的秒針 劃過天際的彗星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.55,0:00:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現今社會人心貧瘠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.20,0:00:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南的推理是一帖良藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.17,0:00:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天故事發生在度假飯店中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.97,0:00:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這起大事件將分成三集播出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.80,0:00:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.45,0:00:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.60,0:00:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.57,0:00:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.86,0:01:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗夜公爵殺人事件(事件篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.89,0:01:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.53,0:01:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼熱的夏天為什麼一定要到這麼熱的地方來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.40,0:01:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實會到這個地方來都是因為博士的一通電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.17,0:01:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊豆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.35,0:02:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 去伊豆的飯店住三天兩夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.63,0:02:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過住宿是全部免費的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.37,0:02:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去嘛 去嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.68,0:02:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免費的話還可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.64,0:02:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到這種地方到底要幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.91,0:02:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在儘快找到那些把我的身體變小的神秘黑衣人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.94,0:02:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是最要緊的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.47,0:02:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.99,0:02:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾放個假也不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.51,0:02:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 柯南 你也來游泳呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.56,0:02:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啊 快點來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.03,0:02:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就別苛求了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.03,0:02:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說只付了一半的錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.02,0:02:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿笠先生預定了三個名額對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.20,0:02:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會有錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.42,0:02:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能 你再仔細的查查看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.45,0:02:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.42,0:02:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.33,0:02:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯店的錢居然只付了一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.83,0:03:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛 我們付另一半就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.71,0:03:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我沒有帶那麼多錢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.68,0:03:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 博士跟我說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.59,0:03:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯店真的是免費的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.10,0:03:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是新一的話當然是免費的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.31,0:03:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我 什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.39,0:03:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.73,0:03:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近在我們這個學者群之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.12,0:03:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢開始流行用電腦通信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.97,0:03:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的朋友裡面有人開始藉由電腦通信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.13,0:03:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所組成的討論會舉辦了一個旅行團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.82,0:03:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就來問我要不要參加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.76,0:03:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個旅行叫做伊豆懸疑之旅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.60,0:03:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懸疑之旅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.88,0:03:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就幫我和一個同事還有他的孫女報了名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.98,0:03:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果順利中選了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.84,0:03:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他的孫女卻因為感冒一直沒有痊癒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.64,0:03:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會不得已把這個機會讓給你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.86,0:03:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次旅行團的參加者連你們總共六組有十個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.40,0:03:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住宿費則是減半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.40,0:03:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過除了你們七個人以外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.05,0:03:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次旅行團的主辦人就混裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.17,0:03:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能找出來的話那住宿費就全免
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.62,0:04:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外還可以得到一份存有某個秘密程式的神秘磁片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.57,0:04:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那個程式的磁片對你應該是沒用的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.33,0:04:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底該怎麼找呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.77,0:04:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼知道這個神秘的主辦人是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.59,0:04:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.80,0:04:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加者的名字跟飯店房間號碼都會告訴所有的團員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.63,0:04:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這個主辦人會假扮成某個人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.66,0:04:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個旅行團裡面引發幾次的意外事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.02,0:04:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某個人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.58,0:04:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.30,0:04:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會以你很熟悉的一個小說人物出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.99,0:04:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人物的名字就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.48,0:04:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該就是暗夜公爵吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.69,0:04:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3.04秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.27,0:04:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你光是回答我的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.18,0:04:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就需要花這麼多的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.44,0:04:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好做個參考的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.93,0:04:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是住在2002房的今野史郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.86,0:04:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後會慢慢熟悉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.15,0:04:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是這樣就知道公爵的身分就不用麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.74,0:05:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是那個只用2.86秒就回答我的問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.04,0:05:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2101號房的江原先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.78,0:05:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個人到底煩不煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.13,0:05:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出其不意就露出了自己的真實身分也是人之常情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.11,0:05:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是 靜江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.66,0:05:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 老爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.88,0:05:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2001號房的金城先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.16,0:05:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我的問題就用了6.29秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.81,0:05:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也看到了 我的眼睛不是很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.87,0:05:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然間碰到你問我那個問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.97,0:05:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本出乎我意料之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.00,0:05:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 這樣也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.64,0:05:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你的資料對照起來 我現在也可以瞭解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.27,0:05:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那份資料根本就不完全啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.97,0:05:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為裡面缺少了某個人的關鍵資料嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.48,0:05:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.33,0:05:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗夜公爵先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.77,0:05:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳在說什麼 2102號房的上條小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.67,0:05:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0.97秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.71,0:06:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你應該註明你比我的1.48秒還慢了0.97秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.87,0:06:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.36,0:06:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們剛才在說的暗夜公爵是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.53,0:06:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.23,0:06:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是裝得挺像的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.62,0:06:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想 新一爸爸的小說裡面不是常常出現嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.83,0:06:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.15,0:06:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗夜公爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.45,0:06:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我爸爸工藤優作所創造出來了的一個神出鬼沒的怪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.21,0:06:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個活躍在夜間的怪盜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.63,0:06:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的時候還是個冷酷的殺人魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.30,0:06:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的真正身分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.60,0:06:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我爸爸工藤優作還沒有在書裡揭曉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.56,0:06:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 那個自稱是暗夜公爵的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.28,0:06:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這些人裡面嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.61,0:06:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是搞不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.38,0:06:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我要回房去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.40,0:06:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.66,0:06:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那飯店錢怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.48,0:06:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.69,0:06:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得參加的人只有十個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.91,0:06:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我、小蘭跟叔叔三個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡還有五個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.20,0:07:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還差兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.18,0:07:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.37,0:07:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸摸屁股有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.92,0:07:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳好像太瘦了一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.62,0:07:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到這兒來幫叔叔倒杯酒好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.52,0:07:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.69,0:07:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.75,0:07:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 你這是幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.20,0:07:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這句話是我要說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.88,0:07:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.07,0:07:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會是前田聰先生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.64,0:07:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐 妳認識他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.81,0:07:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼認不認識的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.37,0:07:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是連續六年的日本空手道冠軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.03,0:07:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是因為崇拜他才開始學空手道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.92,0:07:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫毛利蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.17,0:07:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我前一陣子曾在市區大會上得到優勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.66,0:07:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個空手道冠軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.03,0:07:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個空手道大會優勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.52,0:07:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒想到會在這個地方跟你見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.97,0:07:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太幸運了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.99,0:07:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣什麼好幸運的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.83,0:07:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個女的是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.61,0:07:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.97,0:07:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來介紹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.12,0:07:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的未婚妻佐山明子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.13,0:07:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要結婚啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.57,0:08:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請妳不要放在心上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.28,0:08:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子這個人就是容易吃醋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.78,0:08:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你就是暗夜公爵吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.90,0:08:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1901號房的前田先生0.75秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.83,0:08:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐山小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.87,0:08:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢伙煩不煩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.08,0:08:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.53,0:08:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們來的應該是兩位博士跟一個念小學的小女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.53,0:08:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為他們沒辦法來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.53,0:08:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才換成我們幾個來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.60,0:08:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才在這裡的那個就是我的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.80,0:08:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是博士 是一個偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.71,0:08:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.00,0:08:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父親叫做毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.35,0:08:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛…毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.84,0:08:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經在新聞上看過他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.59,0:08:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是個名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.68,0:08:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太卑鄙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.80,0:08:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然找了一個名偵探來做代打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.94,0:08:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.03,0:08:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下可能是公爵的人就減少了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.15,0:08:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然毛利小五郎也在這兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.91,0:08:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們最好不要互相洩露秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.82,0:09:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸好像很有名耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.08,0:09:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還不都是我的功勞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.70,0:09:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.78,0:09:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.97,0:09:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.63,0:09:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也回房裡去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.61,0:09:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.64,0:09:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以當大家知道爸爸是個偵探時才會那麼吃驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.34,0:09:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.03,0:09:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我從他們七個人裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.06,0:09:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出那個假扮暗夜公爵的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.95,0:09:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在伊豆海灘就可以完全免費的享受個痛快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.47,0:09:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.62,0:09:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說阿笠博士才會對柯南說這一趟是免費的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.04,0:09:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.43,0:09:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.82,0:09:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界上沒有我毛利小五郎解不了的謎題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.23,0:09:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.51,0:09:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才還在為了沒錢付 吵著不要住在這裡咧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.68,0:09:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 既然是這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.85,0:10:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就立刻開始進行調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.33,0:10:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸還挺有幹勁的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.57,0:10:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看我們就到飯店裡面到處逛逛看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.56,0:10:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.92,0:10:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.48,0:10:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在這個地方待一會兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.91,0:10:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.92,0:10:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就先到下面的紀念品店去看一看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.16,0:10:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我待會兒再過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.03,0:10:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.48,0:10:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過聽到是偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.22,0:10:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼大家那麼吃驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.66,0:10:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是一場遊戲嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.51,0:10:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算真的可以讓住宿免費
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.35,0:10:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼那麼緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.94,0:10:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.96,0:10:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那充滿殺氣的眼神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.79,0:10:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得博士對我說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.56,0:10:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外還可以得到一片神秘程式的磁片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.10,0:10:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我想那個磁片對你沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.78,0:10:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼覺得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.52,0:10:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一種不祥的預感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.66,0:11:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯之後再打電話跟博士把事情問清楚好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.74,0:11:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗夜公爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.72,0:11:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.67,0:11:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳池
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.38,0:11:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.80,0:11:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.99,0:11:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.42,0:11:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道那個傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.80,0:12:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在廁所裡面換了衣服從樓梯逃走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.27,0:12:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是暗夜公爵到底是誰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.64,0:12:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行團的團員除了我、小蘭跟叔叔一共只有七個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.63,0:12:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個旅行團的目的 是為了找出混在裡面的主辦人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.40,0:12:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這個主辦人會在旅行期間引發一些事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.44,0:12:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這只是一場單純能讓贏的人住宿費全免的遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.60,0:12:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來說 會有人為了一場遊戲把人推下樓嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.97,0:12:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問我那個程式啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.03,0:12:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個程式到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.26,0:12:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.30,0:12:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連旅行團的召集廣告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.25,0:12:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只是寫了秘密程式這幾個字而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.19,0:12:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.39,0:12:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來要跟我一起參加旅行團的博士說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.62,0:12:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跟我說病毒如何如何的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.80,0:12:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.16,0:12:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這也就奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.76,0:12:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他應該也只知道那是秘密程式而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.79,0:13:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.76,0:13:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個病毒難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.60,0:13:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.23,0:13:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.44,0:13:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.26,0:13:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在紀念品店那裡等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.98,0:13:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 怎麼全身都濕了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.40,0:13:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為剛才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.28,0:13:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我滑了一跤所以就掉到游泳池裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.22,0:13:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你笑什麼笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.99,0:13:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個傻瓜到底是怎麼搞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.99,0:13:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子好像沒有受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.41,0:13:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點把衣服換了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.54,0:13:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去吃飯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.76,0:13:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人好多哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.44,0:13:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.37,0:13:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.66,0:13:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭 我在這兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.25,0:13:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.89,0:13:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有前田先生、佐山小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.14,0:13:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們三個怎麼會在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.73,0:13:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父親現在正在盤問我們兩個人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.10,0:13:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在懷疑我們兩個是不是暗夜公爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.81,0:14:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子小姐這身衣服好漂亮哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.34,0:14:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.66,0:14:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過妳可要多加小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.05,0:14:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為一個不小心說不定就會有色狼攻擊妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.37,0:14:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個色老頭也不覺得膩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.35,0:14:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是明子小姐報名這個旅行團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.38,0:14:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們才來參加的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.94,0:14:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子她一直是工藤優作頭號的小說迷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.23,0:14:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且她對暗夜公爵更是迷得不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.37,0:14:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是關於暗夜公爵的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.85,0:14:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定不會輸給別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.56,0:14:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連我的髮型也剪成像他的短髮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.92,0:14:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對暗夜公爵熟悉的人可不是只有妳一個人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.05,0:14:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.87,0:14:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳只要知道這點就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.85,0:14:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.65,0:14:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好性感的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.36,0:14:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是因為這樣子媽媽才會跑掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.99,0:15:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要看到什麼時候 阿聰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.59,0:15:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件衣服的確不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.00,0:15:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要這樣子 這位客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.98,0:15:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個色老頭看都沒看一眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.94,0:15:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不就喜歡這個嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.54,0:15:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個老先生我記得是2001號房的金城先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.72,0:15:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫作靜江的女人好像不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.41,0:15:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我先去試探一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.63,0:15:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裡 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.45,0:15:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去上廁所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.72,0:15:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你喝得太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.14,0:15:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺也想要找那個電腦病毒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.26,0:15:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是1902房的江戶川柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.79,0:15:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.93,0:15:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事你是從哪兒聽來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.00,0:15:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加旅行團的人每個人都知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.83,0:15:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在說病毒病毒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.77,0:15:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不知道大家為什麼要說這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.55,0:15:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家事實上也不過知道是秘密程式不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.28,0:15:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是個名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.41,0:16:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經有個叫做虛幻的電腦病毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.53,0:16:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢地侵入各個大企業的電腦進行破壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.37,0:16:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然那是一個根本無從發現 也無所阻止的完美程式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.02,0:16:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個病毒太神出鬼沒了 所以才被稱做…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.91,0:16:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗夜公爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.52,0:16:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗…暗夜公爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.36,0:16:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這對於玩電腦的人來說是個人盡皆知的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.45,0:16:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.82,0:16:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行團的主辦人的名字也是暗夜公爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.46,0:16:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了讓大家以為那磁片的內容就是那個病毒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.29,0:16:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個名字讓我想起了一件事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.83,0:16:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它讓我想起了我四年前死去的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.49,0:16:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兒子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.64,0:16:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.55,0:16:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.62,0:16:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 老爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.51,0:16:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳可要小心了 靜江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.75,0:16:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個小鬼可沒那麼簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.78,0:17:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 老爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.95,0:17:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是2002號房的今野先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.57,0:17:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像在打電話的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.56,0:17:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道說些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.57,0:17:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.38,0:17:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來就是江原時男啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.52,0:17:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江原時男
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.11,0:17:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個色老頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.80,0:17:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家說的駭客原來就是他呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.41,0:17:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駭客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.68,0:17:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是擅自將電腦的資料偷出去的那種駭客嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.16,0:17:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.63,0:17:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想有一台這樣的電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.72,0:17:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要亂碰里美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.45,0:17:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里美…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我去年過世的母親的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.48,0:17:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒有事吧 里美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.94,0:17:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.65,0:17:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢伙竟然會給電腦取他母親的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.31,0:17:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個老色鬼不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.49,0:18:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 剛才坐在這裡的人到哪裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.44,0:18:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位先生他說有事情就回到房裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.17,0:18:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟 如果你認識他的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.55,0:18:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你把這個交給他好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.09,0:18:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他把它忘在這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.80,0:18:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是那個人一直繞在頭上的領帶嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.64,0:18:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.23,0:18:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.23,0:18:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.69,0:18:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個孩子就是喜歡到處亂跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.80,0:18:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.02,0:18:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸跟前田先生、明子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.45,0:18:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們都已經回房間去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.24,0:18:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸好像還沒有回來的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.97,0:18:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.43,0:18:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣 讓我進去嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 負心漢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.21,0:18:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是喝太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.19,0:18:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.29,0:18:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在怪我剛才對一個女服務生拋媚眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.12,0:18:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本來就有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.58,0:18:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.04,0:18:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看在明子心情好轉之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.92,0:18:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是到頂樓的休息室去好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.15,0:18:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起去怎麼樣 小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.32,0:19:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我們不要管她好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.78,0:19:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.92,0:19:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.55,0:19:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頂樓展望台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.97,0:19:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美的星空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.26,0:19:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是不能跟妳比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.31,0:19:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.75,0:19:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借過一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.52,0:19:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海水好黑哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.06,0:19:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海水到了晚上真的好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.70,0:19:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.41,0:19:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.66,0:19:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟明子小姐是什麼時候認識的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.42,0:19:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們從小就認識的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.85,0:19:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟她哥哥是無話不談的好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.93,0:19:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是三年前他就已經死掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.55,0:19:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說明子小姐的哥哥已經死掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.01,0:19:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼碰到的都是這種人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.57,0:19:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.97,0:19:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道叔叔到底到哪裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.64,0:19:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才還看到他跟那個女的在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.94,0:20:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是2102號房的上條小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.33,0:20:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.36,0:20:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又多了一個無藥可救的色狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.06,0:20:09.91,DCX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(公主飯店二樓翡翠酒吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.80,0:20:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.70,0:20:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 原來你已經結婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.15,0:20:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我在三年前就離婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.87,0:20:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟這麼一個大美人分開 太可惜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.56,0:20:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們別說這個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.17,0:20:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也差不多可以告訴我了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.36,0:20:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定已經知道誰才是暗夜公爵了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.86,0:20:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.62,0:20:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是關係到飯店房錢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.32,0:20:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我一點提示也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.19,0:20:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你 名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.33,0:20:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.17,0:20:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是的 你口風真緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.41,0:20:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子今天會有個快樂的夜晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.69,0:20:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我看我也該回房間去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.48,0:20:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去快回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.85,0:20:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想明子應該已經冷靜下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.32,0:21:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我如果繼續待在妳身邊的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.43,0:21:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他可能就會咬我了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.55,0:21:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這位小保鏢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.80,0:21:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 待會見啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.10,0:21:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…你知道病毒是什麼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.91,0:21:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.06,0:21:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒的那個病毒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.03,0:21:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我沒問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.69,0:21:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛問這麼奇怪的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.91,0:21:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設計完全沒有瑕疵的電腦病毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.29,0:21:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗夜公爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.96,0:21:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人能利用它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.49,0:21:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以對銀行或大企業進行難以估計的巨額勒索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.35,0:21:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許到這兒來的人裡有不少人的目的就是在此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.72,0:21:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 找了這麼多人來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.21,0:21:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個旅行團的主辦人到底想要幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.27,0:21:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真的只是一個遊戲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.88,0:21:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.30,0:23:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.61,0:23:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.96,0:23:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.29,0:23:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到不死怪人暗夜公爵竟然死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.42,0:23:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太不小心了
